The page shows the main details of a city in this case Glasgow.

At the top there's a gallery of images submitted by the users of the site showing the main attractions and venues in the city.

Below there's a brief history of the city with a link leading to Wikipedia showing the full history of Glasgow.

Underneath we have different categories for things to do like restaurants, museums, events.

At the bottom, a list of top rated tours created by the community.

*** NEW FEATURE ***

Hotel recommendations